WEBVTT

NOTE Paragraph

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.950
Densely packed with surprises waiting around every turn

00:00:08.010 --> 00:00:10.300
Venice is a city to lose yourself in.

00:00:10.505 --> 00:00:12.675
Soak up the Sun with a stroll through

00:00:12.715 --> 00:00:15.795
the city's 400 bridges and dozens of waterways.

00:00:16.025 --> 00:00:20.025
You'll find expansive public squares and hidden beauties in quiet corners

00:00:20.085 --> 00:00:21.605
waiting to be discovered.

00:00:21.765 --> 00:00:24.445
Marvel at the perfectly preserved medieval and

00:00:24.510 --> 00:00:26.120
Renaissance architecture,

00:00:26.185 --> 00:00:28.695
and masterpieces of art in craftsmanship or

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.070
learn a little about the city's long history

00:00:31.125 --> 00:00:34.025
as an important Mediterranean port and art capital.

00:00:34.125 --> 00:00:42.520
Venice's beauty and unique way of life just begs to be explored.